org.hibernate.ogm.transaction.impl

Class ForwardingTransactionImplementor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.ogm.transaction.impl.ForwardingTransactionImplementor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TransactionImplementor, Transaction
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ErrorHandlerEnabledTransactionDecorator

    public class ForwardingTransactionImplementor
extends Object
implements TransactionImplementor
    A TransactionImplementor delegating all methods to another TransactionImplementor instance. Useful as a base class for implementations which need to customize/amend the behavior of the underlying implementation.
    Author:
    Gunnar Morling
